:{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"How do I control my Apōllō Floor Lamp?","answer":"<p>The Apōllō Floor Lamp can be effortlessly controlled using its touch-sensitive remote control, designed for ease and precision. Here's how to make the most of its features:<\/p><p><strong>- Select Colors: <\/strong>Choose from over 1 million colors to perfectly match your mood or space.<\/p><p><strong>- Explore Multicolor Effects:<\/strong> Access 330+ multicolor effects to create dynamic lighting experiences.<\/p><p><strong>- Adjust Multicolor Effects Speed: <\/strong>Use the controls to increase or decrease the speed of multicolor transitions.<\/p><p><strong>- Pause Multicolor Effects: <\/strong>Start, stop, or pause the lighting effects at any time to focus on your favorite display.<\/p><p><strong>- Dim the Light:<\/strong> Adjust the brightness to your desired level for a customizable ambiance.<br\/><br\/>Whether you're looking to set a calming tone or energize your environment, the touch-sensitive remote control puts all the Apōllō Floor Lamp's capabilities in your hands.<\/p>","icon":"none"}},"question_tVFkFE":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Is the Apōllō Floor Lamp worldwide compatible?","answer":"<p>The Apōllō Floor Lamp is worldwide compatible. It supports a wide voltage range of 100V–240V, ensuring safe and reliable operation in any region.<\/p><p>Additionally, it features UL-listed power plugs and includes adapters for US, AU, UK, and EU outlets, adhering to strict safety standards.<\/p><p>With its global compatibility, the Apōllō Floor Lamp offers versatility and peace of mind wherever you are.<\/p>","icon":"none"}},"question_yXrtR9":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"How long will my Apōllō Floor Lamp last?","answer":"<p>Our high quality LEDs that are used for all of our lighting products have a general life expectancy of 50,000+ hours.<\/p><p>If you use any of our lighting products for 10 hours a day, our product will last for at least 13+ years.<\/p>","icon":"none"}},"question_a3LUQT":{"type":"question","settings":{"question":"Do you offer Warranty on the Apōllō Floor Lamp?","answer":"<p>Casa Di Lumo is always committed to ensuring outstanding customer service and a positive experience. We are more than pleased to offer our customers a 2-Year warranty on product malfunctions.<\/p><p>Our Casa Guarantee entitles you to a full replacement or refund of the product unless intentionally damaged.<\/p><p>In the event Casa Di Lumo no longer carries the product, you will be permitted to exchange your piece for another of equal value<\/p>","icon":"none"}}},"block_order":["category_eGyUiX","question_CwGTmT","question_tVFkFE","question_yXrtR9","question_a3LUQT"],"name":"FAQ Page v2","settings":{"auto_hide":true,"layout_style":"tabs-top","content_align":"left","title":"Frequently Asked Questions","subtitle":"Everything you need to know about our premium lighting collection","badge_text":"Support","show_search":false,"contact_title":"Still have questions?","contact_text":"Our team is here to help you find the perfect lighting solution.","contact_email":"hello@seoulglow.com","contact_page_url":"","contact_page_label":"Contact Us","color_bg":"#050505","color_text":"#ffffff","color_muted":"#a3a3a3","color_accent_primary":"#000000","color_accent_secondary":"#000000","color_hero_title":"#ffffff","color_hero_subtitle":"","color_hero_badge_bg":"","color_hero_badge_text":"#ffffff","color_nav_bg":"","color_nav_text":"","color_nav_active_bg":"","color_nav_active_text":"","color_card_bg":"#ffffff0a","color_card_border":"#ffffff14","color_question_text":"","color_answer_text":"","color_chevron":"","color_category_title":"","color_icon":"","color_stats_number":"","color_stats_label":"","color_stats_star":"#fbbf24","color_cta_bg":"","color_cta_text":"","color_cta_btn_bg":"","color_cta_btn_text":"#ffffff","padding_top":20,"padding_bottom":60}},"1773071360cf08f527":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"stamped_reviews_main_widget_eMbbGN"